response.overview: A film shot in Cuba in 1970-1971 about two brigades of 500 Americans that went to Cuba in order to show support by breaking the blockade and to help with the sugar harvest of ten million tons. This is the story of their boat ride from St. Johns, Canada and their stay in Cuba.
response.tagline: A film shot in Cuba in 1970-1971 about two brigades of 500 Americans that went to Cuba in order to show support by breaking the blockade and to help with the sugar harvest of ten million tons.
response.title: Venceremos Brigade (Newsreel)
